{"attribution":"Federal Emergency Management Agency, Ready.gov, Floods, Simplified Chinese; no FEMA, DHS, or U.S. Government endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-001","input":"洪水就是大水暂时溢出到通常干燥的土地上，是美国最常见的自然灾害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-002","input":"不撤离洪水淹没的地区或进入洪水能导致受伤或死亡。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-003","input":"由雨、雪、沿海风暴、风暴潮及大坝和其他水系统溢流造成。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-004","input":"缓慢或快速发展。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-005","input":"山洪暴发可能毫无征兆。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-006","input":"造成停电、中断交通、损坏建筑物并造成山体滑坡。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-007","input":"立即寻找安全的庇护所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-008","input":"切勿步行、游泳或驾车穿越洪水。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-009","input":"离开，别淹死了！","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-010","input":"切记：只需 6 英寸的流水就能击倒人，而 1 英尺流水就能将车辆冲走。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-011","input":"不要靠近快速流动水面上的桥梁。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-012","input":"根据洪水类型：获知撤离时，务必撤离。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-013","input":"去到更高的地面或更高的楼层。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-014","input":"访问 FEMA 洪水地图服务中心，了解所在地区的洪水风险类型。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-015","input":"注册社区警告系统。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-016","input":"紧急警示系统 (EAS) 和国家海洋和大气管理局 (NOAA) 气象无线电也提供紧急情况警示。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-017","input":"购买或更新洪水保单。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-018","input":"房屋保险保单不包括洪水。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-019","input":"保单生效通常需要长达 30 天的时间，因此购买时间应在灾害发生之前。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-020","input":"从国家洪水保险计划 (NFIP) 购买洪水保险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-021","input":"制定一个计划供家庭（包括宠物）使用，以便您和您的家人知道该做什么、去哪里及您需要什么来保护自己免受洪水侵害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-022","input":"学习和演习疏散路线、庇护所计划和山洪暴发响应。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-023","input":"备好几天的用品，包括不易腐烂的食物、清洁用品和用水，以防必须立即离开或所在地区服务中断。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-024","input":"将重要文件放在防水容器中。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-025","input":"创建密码保护的数字副本。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-025","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-026","input":"将贵重物品移至更高处。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-026","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-027","input":"清理排水管和檐沟。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-027","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-028","input":"考虑用电池的液下泵。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-028","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-029","input":"获知要撤离时，立即撤离。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-029","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-030","input":"切勿开车绕过路障。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-030","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-031","input":"当地的响应者用来将交通安全地引出洪水区。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-031","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-032","input":"如果生病并需要就医，请联系医护人员。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-032","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-033","input":"如果可能，请等待进一步的医护服务说明和适当的庇护所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-033","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-034","input":"收听 EAS、NOAA 天气广播或当地警示系统，了解有关洪水的最新紧急信息和说明。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-034","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-035","input":"快速的流水能在毫无警告就冲走桥梁。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-035","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-036","input":"如果车被困在快速的流水中，待在车内。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-036","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-037","input":"如果车内有水上升，爬到车顶上。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-037","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-038","input":"如果被困在建筑物中，上到最高层。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-038","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-039","input":"仅在必要时上到屋顶，上去后发出求救信号。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-039","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-040","input":"不要爬上封闭的阁楼，以免被不断上升的洪水困住。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-040","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-041","input":"注意有关当局的信息和说明。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-041","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-042","input":"只有在当局说安全时才能回家。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-042","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-043","input":"除非有紧急情况，否则要避免开车。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-043","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-044","input":"在清理过程中，应戴上重型工作手套、防护服和靴子，并在清理霉菌或其他杂物时戴好适当的面罩或口罩。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-044","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-045","input":"如患哮喘和其他肺部疾病和/或免疫抑制，则不应进入室内有可以看到或闻到漏水或霉菌生长的建筑物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-045","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-046","input":"儿童不应参加灾后清理工作。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-046","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-047","input":"请注意，蛇和其他动物可能在您的房屋中。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-047","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-048","input":"注意电击的危险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-048","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-049","input":"如果电器设备潮湿或您站在水中，请勿触摸。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-049","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-050","input":"如果安全，要关闭电源以防触电。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-050","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-051","input":"避免踏入洪水中，水可能已被污染，并含有危险的碎屑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-051","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-052","input":"地下或掉落的电线也可能给水导电。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-052","split":"article"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1/sentence-053","input":"仅在室外且远离窗户的地方使用发电机或其他汽油动力机械。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.ready.gov/zh-hans/floods","source_case_id":"sentence-053","split":"article"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"ready-gov-floods-zh-hans-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted only complete Simplified Chinese paragraph and list-item sentences from the checksum-pinned Ready.gov main element, removed navigation, images, external resources, phone/URL instructions, page furniture, and exact duplicates, and added input-only provenance; no expected text or converter output was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"article":53},"eligible_pending_review":53,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":53},"upstream_revision":"Ready.gov Simplified Chinese Floods; page last updated 2025-10-22; retrieved HTML SHA-256: 212da67b2ec70dfd32b7b88a5e546f3c551390d9f2ce7c8591deab7db3972e27","version":1}
